" Return to last edit position when opening files (You want this!) '\" is the cursor position when last exiting the current buffer {{{2
autocmd BufReadPost *
     \ if line("'\"") > 0 && line("'\"") <= line("$") |
     \   exe "normal! g`\"" |
     \ endif

